headline: MarketAxess Reports Record Trading Week in U.S. Government Bonds, including $100+ Billion Record Day
summary: NEW YORK, April 14, 2025--MarketAxess Holdings Inc. (Nasdaq: MKTX), the operator of a leading electronic trading platform for fixed-income securities, today announced that its Rates business reported an all-time single-day record of $102.3 billion U.S. Government Bonds notional traded on April 9.
